     F** ECSR56 **********************************
     F* DIE INVENTORY LIST
     F* PROGRAM ID. : ECSR56
     F* CREATE DATE. : OCT.01.02                 *
     F* AUTHOR.         : TCH                    *
     F********************************** ECSR55 **
     FECSPW56 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FAB#PPCT UF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *-----------------------------------------------------------
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *--------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *--------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           @CHK    1
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @CHK
     C                     MOVEL'ECSR55  'K@KWD   8 P
     C           K@KWD     CHAINAB#PPCT              90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           CTCHR1    ANDNE*BLANK
     C                     MOVE '1'       @CHK
     C                     EXFMTWIN01
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL#USER     CTCHR1
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CLEARAB#PPCT1
     C                     MOVELK@KWD     CTKEY1
     C                     WRITEAB#PPCT1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     UPDATAB#PPCT1
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *
